Class ContextMenu

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TagBase, GlobalAttribute, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class ContextMenu
extends AbstractAttribute
implements GlobalAttribute
    <element contextmenu="menu_id"> 
     
 The contextmenu attribute specifies a context menu for an element. The context menu appears when a user right-clicks on the element.
 
 The value of the contextmenu attribute is the id of the  element to open.
